">public</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"在其它仓库部署\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#在其它仓库部署\"></a> 在其它仓库部署</h3>\n<p>需要提前准备一个具有 Repo 权限的 Access Token。</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"yml\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">Deploy</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">uses:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">JamesIves/github-pages-deploy-action@v4</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">with:</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">token:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">$&#123;&#123; secrets.DEPLOY_TO_USER_REPOSITORY &#125;&#125;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">repository-name:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">example/example.github.io</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">folder:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">public</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"在非根目录部署\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#在非根目录部署\"></a> 在非根目录部署</h2>\n<h3 id=\"重新打包主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#重新打包主题\"></a> 重新打包主题</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/HexoThemeNaive\">Hexo Theme Naive</a> 的 <a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/HexoThemeNaive/releases\">Release</a> 使用了默认的公共目录 <code>/</code>，在非根目录部署时需要重新打包。</p>\n<p>如果你需要部署在 <code>site</code> 目录下，可以执行以下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"plain\">npm install\nnpx cross-env VUE_PUBLIC_PATH=/site/ vue-cli-service build\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"修改-root\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#修改-root\"></a> 修改 Root</h3>\n<p>在 config.yml 中设置 <code>root</code> 字段，如果你需要部署在 <code>site</code> 目录下，可以这样设置：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"yml\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">root:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/site/</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"修改静态资源路径\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#修改静态资源路径\"></a> 修改静态资源路径</h3>\n<p>可参考<a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/HexoDemoNaive\">此仓库</a>的文件树和静态资源配置。</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"yml\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">favicon:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">favicon.svg</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">avatar:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/HexoDemoNaive/assets/avatar.svg</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">bgm:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/HexoDemoNaive/assets/standard-jazz-bars.mp3</span>\n</code></pre>\n","length":"902","time":"4min","categories":["Hexo"],"tags":["Config","NodeJS"]}